               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300916-354-cd1825" type="crimeDate">10th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-354-off1824 t18300916-354-cd1825"></join>, 1 coat, value 15s.; 1 pair of trousers, value 13s., and 1 waistcoat, value 5s
            </rs>., the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-354-victim2876" type="victimName">
